<D>__{it was father tomassino they were trying to kill.}
<A>__{bonifacia starts softly to cry. nico puts his hand on her shoulder, comforting her.}
<C>__{nico}
<D>__{where is tomassino? where is he now?}
<A>__{the nun shakes her head. nico looks to the refugees. they don't know, either.}
<C>__{refugee man}
<D>__{he run, mister. he go }
<A>__{he gestures: "who knows where?"}
<C>__{nico}
